{"tid":982343,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺啲陷家剷食野雪雪聲習習聲好撚煩","createTime":"2019-01-15T05:07:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T11:49:17.000Z","uid":137217,"like":53,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a064800caa352a6e645e3690cf9fb6659f9b3c9d","tid":982343,"uid":137217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T05:07:09.000Z","msg":"有個舊同事真係好撚癡線<br />\n只要經過佢個口既動作一撚定有聲<br />\n叮個飯佢用玻璃兜<br />\n下下都匙更撈底亨到個兜底<br />\n然後擺落個口度又可以有更撞牙齒既聲<br />\n跟住要雪一聲吸啲飯落個口度<br />\n然後再習習習<br />\n你老母個撚樣一食飯就比佢咁轟炸半粒鐘<br />\n然後飲水又係牙撞樽<br />\n然後咕咕咕咁飲<br />\n飲完仲一定要ah咁<br />\n唔撚知以為你飲緊有氣<br />\n蒸餾水嚟架仆街<br />\n真係好撚無家教<br />\n然後岩岩一個大陸婆係我隔離檯食飯又係咁<br />\n即刻勾起返我呢段回憶<br />\n其實個腦係咪有缺陷,食飯食到咁撚樣"},{"pid":"6674cbd21b1e912b0417eb951446cb563023d61e","tid":982343,"uid":69976,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T05:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i